snippet.title: "a new life." trailer (Steam/Android/iOS)
snippet.description:
Play on Steam (https://store.steampowered.com/app/1297160/a_new_life); iOS (https://apps.apple.com/us/app/a-new-life/id1512500246); and Android (https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.AngelaHe.anewlife).

Weee another game! This one's inspired by my experiences at home, in college, etc from the past few years.  Hope it gives you fuzzy feelings ^_^
